Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
read_spdf(25.10)                                              read_spdf(25.10)

Name
       read_spdf  - Reads the statistical parameter distribution format (SPDF)
       file

Syntax
       read_spdf

       {-help]

       <SPDF_file_name>

       Reads the statistical parameter distribution  format  (SPDF)  file.  An
       SPDF  file  contains statistics of variation of process parameters. The
       SPDF file is required for statistical static timing analysis (SSTA).

Parameters
       -help  Prints out the command usage.

       <SPDF_file_name>
              Specifies the name of a SPDF file - that contains statistics  of
              variation of process parameters.

